# Grocery Billing Software — Walkthrough

## What Was Built

A **fully self-contained grocery shop billing app** built with Vanilla HTML + CSS + JavaScript. No build tools, no backend, no installation required — just open [index.html](file:///c:/Users/Tarun/OneDrive/Desktop/Antigravity/index.html) in any browser.

## Project Structure

```
Antigravity/
├── index.html              ← App shell: sidebar, topbar, modals
└── src/
    ├── style.css           ← Full design system (dark theme, glassmorphism)
    ├── db.js               ← localStorage data layer + 24 seed products
    ├── invoice.js          ← Invoice HTML builder + print popup
    ├── main.js             ← SPA router, sidebar toggle, clock, toasts
    └── pages/
        ├── dashboard.js    ← Stats, SVG revenue chart, top products
        ├── billing.js      ← POS: grid, cart, discount, hold bills, calculator
        ├── products.js     ← CRUD table, cost/profit, stock adjustments
        ├── customers.js    ← CRM table, loyalty points, purchase history
        ├── reports.js      ← GST, revenue, category, stock, and profit reports
        ├── history.js      ← Paginated bill history, date filter, reprint
        └── settings.js     ← Shop info, accent color, backup/restore data
```

## Features

| Page | Features |
|---|---|
| **Dashboard** | Revenue stats **+ Profit margin**, 7-day chart, top products, recent bills, **Low stock alerts banner** |
| **New Bill (POS)** | Product grid, cart, discount, **Customer autofill & link, Cash/Change Calculator, Hold Bills & Resume, Payment Mode**, printable invoice |
| **Products** | Sortable table, **Cost price & profit margin column**, add/edit modal, **Stock adjustments modal + history**, CSV export |
| **Customers** | **NEW: Customer CRM table, Loyalty points (1 pt/₹10), Add/Edit modal, Purchase history drill-down panel** |
| **Reports** | **NEW: 5 tabs (GST collected by tax bracket, Monthly revenue + 7-day profit, Category revenue, Low stock status + movement log, Profit margin by product)** |
| **Bill History** | Paginated table (15/page), date-range filter, search, click-to-view invoice, reprint button, **Payment Mode display** |
| **Settings** | Shop info, tax rate, currency, accent color picker, **Data Backup (export JSON) & Restore (import JSON)**, clear bills/products |

